- **obra/superpowers** — the most-loved general agentic-engineering skills suite (TDD, systematic debugging, planning, code review)
- **pbakaus/impeccable** — design-polish skills (typeset, layout, normalize, harden, polish, critique) that materially improve any design output$md$, null, 'https://skills.sh');
